The paper discusses the need for mechanisms to tie RDF data to quality guarantees, which is a common concern in database systems (cs.DB). The paper also proposes a language for specifying instance-level data constraints, which is related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) as it involves reasoning about data. The paper also discusses the impact on query engines and query formulation, which is relevant to software engineering (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL).
